00:41:54,732 --> 00:41:56,692
No, Your Honor.

805
00:41:56,903 --> 00:42:00,753
Miss Cabot, does the District 
Attorney plan to contest the findings?

806
00:42:00,753 --> 00:42:02,203
Not at this time, Your Honor.

807
00:42:02,203 --> 00:42:04,585
The People are satisfied
with the doctor's report.

808
00:42:04,585 --> 00:42:07,996
Then I rule the defendant
Daniel Stephen Varney...

809
00:42:07,996 --> 00:42:10,325
not competent to assist
in his own defense...

